#Instalation steps#
###################
1)Follow tutorial on unisoft website.
    1.1)Install Sql Server 2012. ?????????
    1.2)Open SQL Server Management Studio <<1)right click on Security ->Logins->set input for login name
                                            ->set input for SQL Server authentication
                                            ->deactivate  Enforce password policy.
                                            2)set master as  Default Database
                                            3)set dbcreator Server Roles.
    1.3)Connect Kefalaio to SQL Server  «Οργάνωση – Σύστημα» run «SQL Server setup».
    1.4)Create company from Kefalaio with sql Server enabled.

2)Configure database.xml







